<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/index2.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Easy Cooking</a>
        <a href="#">About Us</a>
        <a href="#">Explore Recipes</a>
        <button class="sign-btn"><a href="/login" class="btn-text">Sign Up</a></button>
    </nav>
    <div class="principal">
        <div class="transparency">
            <div class="text">
                <h1 class="title">Easy Cooking</h1>
                <p>Stop wasting your time while thinking what to cook.
                    We can help you to create your own recipes from products which are in your fridge right now!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="div-all">
        <h1 class="title-how">How it works?</h1>
        <div class="works">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="img"><img src="/images/groceriesIcon.png" alt="" class="img-fridge">></div>
                <div class="card-title"><h2>Look in your fridge</h2></div>
                <div class="card-text"><p>Check what do you have in your fridge. While from 1 to 10 words in search field and you find the recipes with these ingredients.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="img"><img src="/images/recipeIcon1.png" alt="" class="img-recipe"></div>
                <div class="card-title"><h2>Choose a recipe</h2></div>
                <div class="card-text"><p>Choose the best one for you. We want you to make the process of cooking easier for you.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="img"><img src="/images/spaghettiIcon.png" alt="" class="img-spaghetti"></div>
                <div class="card-title"><h2>Enjoy your dish!</h2></div>
                <div class="card-text">
                    <p>After registration you will have your personal space where you can add recipes. Then, you can enjoy your dish!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="find-btn">Find a recipe</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>